23
00:01:53,840 --> 00:01:55,510
What were you thinking back then?

24
00:01:55,800 --> 00:01:57,650
You just give the workshop
to others like that.

25
00:01:58,950 --> 00:01:59,950
I have the skills.

26
00:02:00,300 --> 00:02:01,920
If the workshop's gone,
I can rebuild it.

27
00:02:02,510 --> 00:02:04,200
But if anything happened to you,

28
00:02:04,920 --> 00:02:06,150
I'd regret it for the rest of my life.

29
00:02:07,120 --> 00:02:10,290
♪Light, etched on the old wall♪

30
