Does the injury on your face hurt?

33
00:02:20,630 --> 00:02:21,560
It's fine.

34
00:02:21,560 --> 00:02:22,480
Let me see.

35
00:02:23,820 --> 00:02:26,460
♪Destiny, mere scattered coins♪

36
00:02:26,470 --> 00:02:27,790
