37
00:02:27,810 --> 00:02:31,480
♪Traded for bolts of red silk♪

38
00:02:33,520 --> 00:02:35,270
Now that you've given them the workshop,

39
00:02:36,080 --> 00:02:37,160
what's next?

40
00:02:39,310 --> 00:02:40,920
We survive on our craftsmanship.

41
00:02:41,310 --> 00:02:42,270
Don't overthink it.

42
00:02:42,430 --> 00:02:43,360
I originally planned

43
00:02:43,520 --> 00:02:45,390
to open a factory in town anyway.

44
00:02:45,870 --> 00:02:47,120
As for machinery,

45
00:02:47,120 --> 00:02:48,550
I'll repair retired equipment

46
00:02:49,120 --> 00:02:50,320
from the steel factory.

47
