were already badly outdated.

49
00:02:54,020 --> 00:02:55,270
I wanted to replace them anyway.

50
00:02:57,400 --> 00:02:58,640
Turn around.

51
00:02:59,630 --> 00:03:00,760
Let me check your wounds.

52
00:03:02,080 --> 00:03:03,920
It's nothing. Just... just scratches.

53
