I just remembered

79
00:04:41,680 --> 00:04:42,910
there's something I haven't finished.

80
00:04:43,800 --> 00:04:44,720
Wait for me.

81
00:04:46,250 --> 00:04:48,170
♪Using love as the sail♪

82
00:04:48,170 --> 00:04:54,170
♪We navigate
through life's joys and sorrows♪

83
00:04:54,720 --> 00:04:58,750
♪No matter how many trials ahead♪

84
00:05:00,400 --> 00:05:01,770
(Xinguang Mold Factory
Transfer Contract)

85
00:05:01,770 --> 00:05:02,600
Dad...

86
00:05:02,920 --> 00:05:04,390
You... you have to believe me.

87
00:05:07,870 --> 00:05:08,830
Believe you?

88
00:05:09,510 --> 00:05:10,680
The police

89
00:05:10,680 --> 00:05:12,350
called my office!

90
00:05:15,190 --> 00:05:17,070
Dad, this... this must be
a misunderstanding.

91
00:05:17,070 --> 00:05:19,120
Look, I have the contract, right?

92
00:05:19,120 --> 00:05:20,830
Payment delivered, goods received.

93
00:05:20,830 --> 00:05:22,070
This is not a problem.

94
00:05:22,070 --> 00:05:23,250
It must be a misunderstanding.

95
00:05:25,070 --> 00:05:26,200
It's a misunderstanding?

96
00:05:27,400 --> 00:05:28,440
If it's a misunderstanding,

97
00:05:28,870 --> 00:05:30,200
clarifying it should suffice.

98
00:05:30,360 --> 00:05:32,000
Yes. If I recall correctly,

99
00:05:32,190 --> 00:05:33,710
you did receive payment, right?

100
00:05:34,030 --> 00:05:34,880
Party Secretary Zhou,

101
00:05:35,270 --> 00:05:36,500
your son kidnapped my wife

102
00:05:36,500 --> 00:05:37,680
and forced me to sign this contract.

103
00:05:37,680 --> 00:05:38,600
No!

104
00:05:39,040 --> 00:05:40,240
Dad, this is too serious!

105
00:05:40,360 --> 00:05:41,390
I didn't do it!

106
00:05:42,390 --> 00:05:43,310
Okay, enough.

107
00:05:43,310 --> 00:05:44,230
Then

108
00:05:44,560 --> 00:05:47,390
both of you report
to the police tomorrow

109
00:05:47,390 --> 00:05:49,560
to clarify this. Understood?

110
00:05:49,560 --> 00:05:50,480
Understood.

111
00:05:53,120 --> 00:05:54,080
Thank you, Dad.

112
00:06:19,310 --> 00:06:20,470
I have the contract.

113
00:06:20,600 --> 00:06:21,800
Still want to fight me?

114
00:06:23,000 --> 00:06:23,920
Pah!

115
00:06:29,600 --> 00:06:30,520
Officer,

116
00:06:30,630 --> 00:06:31,760
any updates about my case?

117
00:06:32,680 --> 00:06:33,680
Comrade,

118
00:06:33,680 --> 00:06:35,320
you did sign the contract,

119
00:06:35,510 --> 00:06:36,640
and he has witnesses.

120
00:06:36,950 --> 00:06:39,760
This matter is now complicated.

121
00:06:40,390 --> 00:06:41,800
But rest assured,

122
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:42,920
we'll keep investigating

123
00:06:42,920 --> 00:06:44,320
what you mentioned.

124
00:06:44,800 --> 00:06:47,270
You can bring new evidence

125
00:06:47,270 --> 00:06:48,350
anytime.

126
00:06:48,600 --> 00:06:51,150
Remember, justice may be delayed,

127
00:06:51,360 --> 00:06:52,510
but never denied.

128
00:06:55,830 --> 00:06:56,750
Thank you.

129
00:07:06,390 --> 00:07:07,310
Here, the money.

130
00:07:08,780 --> 00:07:15,780
(Telephone)

131
00:07:38,040 --> 00:07:41,150
(The mold factory incident
must weigh heavily on Lu Ran.)

132
00:07:42,310 --> 00:07:43,950
(I need to find a way to reassure her.)

133
00:07:56,800 --> 00:07:57,720
Come.

134
00:08:00,160 --> 00:08:01,800
This site is confirmed.

135
00:08:02,040 --> 00:08:02,960
Right here.

136
00:08:03,620 --> 00:08:05,120
I plan to add another set of machines.

137
00:08:05,630 --> 00:08:07,350
I contacted Director Sun.

138
00:08:07,600 --> 00:08:09,000
He has retired equipment.

139
00:08:09,160 --> 00:08:10,040
I've inspected them.

140
00:08:10,040 --> 00:08:11,000
They're repairable.

141
00:08:11,400 --> 00:08:13,290
You're a college graduate
with a broader vision.

142
00:08:13,720 --> 00:08:14,640
Give me some advice.

143
00:08:14,870 --> 00:08:16,360
(Production Safety)
Expanding scale

144
00:08:16,360 --> 00:08:17,640
requires more orders.

145
00:08:18,240 --> 00:08:19,800
Previously, your craftsmanship attracted

146
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:21,880
spontaneous orders,

147
00:08:22,360 --> 00:08:24,510
but that's unstable.

148
00:08:24,630 --> 00:08:25,910
You can't control it.

149
00:08:27,120 --> 00:08:28,320
I've considered this.

150
00:08:28,680 --> 00:08:30,000
The orders are constant now.

151
00:08:30,160 --> 00:08:31,240
But after expansion,

152
00:08:31,390 --> 00:08:33,110
waiting passively won't work.

153
00:08:33,600 --> 00:08:34,790
Our close cooperation partners

154
00:08:34,790 --> 00:08:35,720
have also introduced

155
00:08:35,720 --> 00:08:37,110
many companies.

156
00:08:37,240 --> 00:08:38,230
I'll contact them.

157
00:08:39,270 --> 00:08:41,160
This works short-term,

158
00:08:41,550 --> 00:08:43,080
but long-term we need

159
00:08:43,080 --> 00:08:44,230
our own sales staff,

160
00:08:44,670 --> 00:08:47,990
separate from production.

161
00:08:49,150 --> 00:08:51,080
We're in stable cooperation

162
00:08:51,080 --> 00:08:52,400
with the steel factory.

163
00:08:53,080 --> 00:08:55,840
Partnering with larger

164
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:57,400
and more famous enterprises

165
00:08:57,750 --> 00:08:58,990
will boost our reputation

166
00:08:59,150 --> 00:09:00,920
and orders.

167
00:09:03,270 --> 00:09:04,400
Let's go there.

168
00:09:05,550 --> 00:09:06,470
The office is there.

169
00:09:06,470 --> 00:09:08,150
(Quality First. Safety Production)

170
00:09:08,150 --> 00:09:09,070
Be careful.

171
00:09:27,790 --> 00:09:28,710
Where's everyone?

172
00:09:29,360 --> 00:09:30,270
None of them left.

173
00:09:30,270 --> 00:09:31,350
All... all gone.

174
00:09:32,080 --> 00:09:33,080
All gone?

175
00:09:33,390 --> 00:09:34,310
Right.

176
00:09:35,440 --> 00:09:37,030
As the saying goes,

177
00:09:37,030 --> 00:09:38,680
new reign, new court.

178
00:09:39,030 --> 00:09:40,990
New officials need new moves.

179
00:09:41,300 --> 00:09:42,870
- Yes.
- Naturally, I cleared them out.

180
00:09:43,270 --> 00:09:45,150
- Say that again!
- Boss!

181
00:09:45,150 --> 00:09:46,360
- No...
- Say that again!

182
00:09:46,360 --> 00:09:47,200
Boss!

183
00:09:47,220 --> 00:09:48,120
And you...

184
00:09:48,120 --> 00:09:49,080
Why didn't you stop him?

185
00:09:49,440 --> 00:09:50,480
A workshop without workers

186
00:09:50,480 --> 00:09:51,710
is useless!

187
00:09:52,750 --> 00:09:55,040
I'm ruined!

188
00:09:55,040 --> 00:09:58,300
(Xinguang Mold)

189
00:10:11,550 --> 00:10:12,590
Come here, brothers.

190
00:10:16,600 --> 00:10:18,240
Who knows
what Zhou Huacheng was thinking

191
00:10:18,240 --> 00:10:19,720
when he asked
for Brother Qi's old workshop?

192
00:10:20,080 --> 00:10:21,000
Yeah.

193
00:10:21,320 --> 00:10:22,400
I had planned

194
00:10:22,870 --> 00:10:24,510
to move old equipment here

195
00:10:24,510 --> 00:10:25,870
and add new machines.

196
00:10:26,150 --> 00:10:27,280
But now only one has arrived.

197
00:10:27,670 --> 00:10:28,840
The other one is coming soon.

198
00:10:28,840 --> 00:10:30,150
Brother Qi works fast.

199
00:10:30,150 --> 00:10:31,840
- Yes.
- Look at our new factory.

200
00:10:31,840 --> 00:10:33,040
Big and spacious.

201
00:10:34,000 --> 00:10:35,870
But I'll cover the second machine's cost

202
00:10:35,870 --> 00:10:36,790
personally.

203
00:10:36,960 --> 00:10:38,230
It's a family business.

204
00:10:38,360 --> 00:10:40,710
Brother Qi, why say that?

205
00:10:40,870 --> 00:10:42,150
You're treating us as outsiders?

206
00:10:42,150 --> 00:10:43,000
Too polite.

207
00:10:43,000 --> 00:10:44,350
We all know about Ran.

208
00:10:44,510 --> 00:10:45,440
Let's shoulder this

209
00:10:45,600 --> 00:10:47,200
together!

210
00:10:47,450 --> 00:10:48,480
Yes, let's do it together.

211
00:10:48,480 --> 00:10:49,870
Brothers,

212
00:10:49,870 --> 00:10:51,230
I appreciate it.

213
00:10:51,650 --> 00:10:53,120
If we brothers want to open a factory,

214
00:10:53,120 --> 00:10:54,520
we have to make sure
business is business,

215
00:10:54,520 --> 00:10:55,260
so that it'll last.

216
00:10:55,510 --> 00:10:56,680
And business partnerships

217
00:10:56,870 --> 00:10:57,960
require clear boundaries.

218
00:10:57,960 --> 00:10:59,680
We understand
you surrendered the workshop

219
00:10:59,840 --> 00:11:00,990
for Ran.

220
00:11:01,150 --> 00:11:02,550
But she's been good to us.

221
00:11:02,550 --> 00:11:03,870
We should share this burden.

222
00:11:04,200 --> 00:11:05,080
- Yes.
- Brother Qi.

223
00:11:05,080 --> 00:11:05,920
Yes, Brother Qi.

224
00:11:05,930 --> 00:11:07,480
We understand your thoughts.

225
00:11:07,480 --> 00:11:08,710
- But...
- This is decided.

226
00:11:09,480 --> 00:11:10,400
Besides,

227
00:11:10,630 --> 00:11:11,800
don't tell Lu Ran about this.

228
00:11:12,390 --> 00:11:13,990
I don't want her to feel guilty.

229
00:11:14,870 --> 00:11:15,790
This...

230
00:11:18,440 --> 00:11:19,360
Okay, Brother.

231
00:11:19,790 --> 00:11:21,750
We won't tell Ran.

232
00:11:21,750 --> 00:11:22,670
Don't worry.

233
00:11:23,390 --> 00:11:24,310
Yes, Brother.

234
00:11:24,440 --> 00:11:25,950
Don't worry, we're here.

235
00:11:26,080 --> 00:11:27,400
Isn't Ran moving out?

236
00:11:27,400 --> 00:11:28,220
Go over there.

237
00:11:28,220 --> 00:11:29,200
We'll handle things here.

238
00:11:29,200 --> 00:11:30,050
- Yes.
- Alright.

239
00:11:30,070 --> 00:11:30,910
Thanks for your hard work.

240
00:11:30,910 --> 00:11:31,820
- Okay.
- Alright, Brother.

241
00:11:31,820 --> 00:11:33,360
- Thanks.
- Be careful, Brother.

242
00:11:34,150 --> 00:11:35,480
Let's start.

243
00:11:35,480 --> 00:11:36,340
- Come on.
- Come on!

244
00:11:36,340 --> 00:11:37,270
Come.

245
00:11:41,030 --> 00:11:42,390
You two,

246
00:11:42,390 --> 00:11:43,350
such big matters

247
00:11:43,480 --> 00:11:44,990
and you didn't tell me!

248
00:11:45,630 --> 00:11:46,550
Come on, Brother.

249
00:11:46,720 --> 00:11:47,720
Mom,

250
00:11:47,720 --> 00:11:49,800
Shengfeng didn't want to trouble you.

251
00:11:50,600 --> 00:11:52,510
Once it's done,

252
00:11:52,510 --> 00:11:53,750
you won't suffer.

253
00:11:53,960 --> 00:11:55,520
And it'll be a surprise.

254
00:11:56,480 --> 00:11:57,920
A surprise indeed.

255
00:11:58,200 --> 00:11:59,120
Yeah, a surprise.

256
00:12:00,320 --> 00:12:02,230
I'm moving to the town
to live in a big house.

257
00:12:03,080 --> 00:12:04,000
Shenggong,

258
00:12:04,270 --> 00:12:06,230
finish packing quickly.

259
00:12:06,230 --> 00:12:07,750
Ma Qiang and the others will come soon.

260
00:12:07,840 --> 00:12:08,800
Let's move then.

261
00:12:11,670 --> 00:12:12,830
I won't join you.

262
00:12:16,910 --> 00:12:17,830
What's wrong?

263
00:12:19,870 --> 00:12:20,790
Why not?

264
00:12:21,120 --> 00:12:23,630
Divorce scrambled your brain?

265
00:12:23,630 --> 00:12:26,280
Mom, I'm over 30 years old.

266
00:12:26,440 --> 00:12:28,630
I can't mooch off my brother anymore.

267
00:12:30,510 --> 00:12:31,390
I won't go.

268
00:12:31,390 --> 00:12:32,800
Brother, what are you saying?

269
00:12:32,900 --> 00:12:34,070
Shengfeng, don't try to convince me.

270
00:12:34,320 --> 00:12:35,470
I know you mean well.

271
00:12:36,200 --> 00:12:37,200
But I'm your brother.

272
00:12:39,360 --> 00:12:40,350
I can't lower myself.

273
00:12:50,050 --> 00:12:51,230
Shengfeng, stop convincing me.

274
00:12:52,240 --> 00:12:53,160
Brother,

275
00:12:53,350 --> 00:12:54,470
I'm not here to convince you.

276
00:12:58,600 --> 00:13:00,480
Lu Ran says you've been running

277
00:13:00,480 --> 00:13:01,470
the cart business lately.

278
00:13:01,840 --> 00:13:02,830
I'll leave it to you.

279
00:13:04,510 --> 00:13:06,560
Just give her dividends
after making money.

280
00:13:09,080 --> 00:13:10,000
Brother,

281
00:13:10,150 --> 00:13:11,110
no matter where you are,

282
00:13:11,960 --> 00:13:12,950
we're still brothers.

283
00:13:14,480 --> 00:13:15,520
I support

284
00:13:16,320 --> 00:13:17,350
your decision.

285
00:13:27,550 --> 00:13:28,560
Take care.

286
00:13:37,380 --> 00:13:42,820
(Oxygen Tank Transport
Service Agreement)

287
00:13:50,630 --> 00:13:51,990
Come on, let me help.

288
00:13:52,150 --> 00:13:53,070
I'll do it.

289
00:13:55,000 --> 00:13:55,920
Be careful.

